{
  "stem": "8775.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by the way, when we went to the ghetto-- and that just shows you how the, the Nazi propaganda afflicted, or affected, the people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People started laughing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And people started cheering.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, I'm talking about the general Hungarian population.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was a sad sight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I-- we were bleeding from the inside because of that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because those were people who perhaps were our-- well, not friends, but our clients and neighbors.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And these were the people who-- and they were hardly waiting for, for the Jews to, to leave their homes so they can rob them, so they can go to their homes and rob them from their possessions and take everything away from them.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because they figured these people will never come back, anyway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My recollection isn't too clear on that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I, I don't even know what I took.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If anything, probably just a pair of slacks or shoes and, you know, coat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I, I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we checked into the ghetto, there were gendarmes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the gendarmes were worse.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was not police.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The gendarme was like more of a military-type operation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was other than Budapest, like in the suburbs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And gendarmes, which we called [HUNGARIAN ]-- these were very vicious people, very vicious people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These were Hungarian gendarmes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were the ones who controlled the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, the, the SS controlled it as well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now in the ghetto, they formed a, like a Jewish committee of the elders.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father's first cousin, another lawyer, was a member-- or I'm not sure-- perhaps president of that Jewish committee.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Csato, C-S-A-T-O, David.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was a first cousin of my husband.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
